snippet.title: Rush - Tom Sawyer (Metal Cover) ft. Andrea Boccarusso
snippet.description:
Hey Folks!

I am so busy getting ready for my own business. However, with a short break I was able to make a nice cover with my Italian friend, Andrea. Projecting my emotions to the music of RUSH was a very new attempt for me and we did not have enough time to polish the video, but I think we got quite interesting results. Please, visit Adreas' channel he will absolutely please you :)

By the way, I'm struggling to make a new series on my YouTube channel. If you like my singing then stay tuned, I'll be back shortly!

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Lead and Harmony Vocals
Andrea Boma Boccarusso (Lock The Basement, Italy) - All Instrumentals and Video Editing
